name: Allay interaction
description: Allow giving and taking items to/from Allay

name: Axolotl Scooping
description: Allow scooping of axolotl using a bucket

name: Block explode damage
description: Allow Bed & Respawn Anchors to break blocks and damage entities.

name: Boats
description: Toggle placing, breaking and entering into boats.

name: Break hoppers
description: Toggle hoppers breaking. Overrides the Break Blocks flag.

name: Break spawners
description: Toggle spawners breaking. Overrides the Break Blocks flag.

name: Change Settings
description: Allow to switch which member role can change island settings.

name: Chests and minecart chests
description: Toggle interaction with chests and chest minecarts. (does not include trapped chests)

name: Clean Super Flat
description: Enable to clean any super-flat chunks in island worlds

name: Coarse dirt tilling
description: Toggle tilling coarse dirt and breaking podzol to obtain dirt

name: All containers
description: Toggle interaction with all containers. Includes: Barrel, bee hive, brewing stand, chest, composter, dispenser, dropper, flower pot, furnace, hopper, item frame, jukebox, minecart chest, shulker box, trapped chest.  Changing individual settings overrides this flag.

name: Creeper griefing protection
description: Toggle creeper griefing protection when ignited by island visitor.

name: Dragon Egg
description: Prevents interaction with Dragon Eggs.  This does not protect it from being placed or broken.

name: Enderman griefing
description: Endermen can remove blocks from islands

name: Entity portal usage
description: Toggles if entities (non-player) can use portals to teleport between dimensions

name: Fire burning
description: Toggle whether fire can burn blocks or not.

name: Fire ignition
description: Toggle whether fire can be ignited by non-player means or not.

name: Fire spread
description: Toggle whether fire can spread to nearby blocks or not.

name: Fish Scooping
description: Allow scooping of fishes using a bucket

name: Flint and steel
description: Allow players to ignite fires or campfires using flint and steel or fire charges.

name: Limit mobs to island
description: Remove mobs that go outside protected island space

name: Item Frame
description: Toggle interaction. Overrides place or break blocks

name: Lecterns
description: Allow to place books on a lectern or to take books from it.  It does not prevent players from reading the books.

name: Limit entity type spawning
description: Limit entities from spawning in this game mode.

name: Liquids flowing outside islands
description: Toggle whether liquids can flow outside of the island's protection range. Disabling it helps avoiding lava and water generating cobblestone in the area between two islands.  Note that liquids will still flow vertically. They will also not spread horizontally if they are placed outside an island's protection range.

name: Minecarts
description: Toggle placing, breaking and entering into minecarts.

name: Natural creature spawning outside range
description: Toggle whether creatures (animals and monsters) can spawn naturally outside an island's protection range.  Note that it doesn't prevent creatures to spawn via a mob spawner or a spawn egg.

name: Obsidian scooping
description: Allow players to scoop up obsidian with an empty bucket back into lava.  This helps the newbies that failed to build their cobblestone generator.  Note: obsidian cannot be scooped up if there are other obsidian blocks within a 2-block radius.

name: Offline Growth
description: When disabled, plants will not grow on islands where all members are offline. May help reduce lag.

name: Offline Redstone
description: When disabled, redstone will not operate on islands where all members are offline. May help reduce lag. Does not affect spawn island.

name: Pets Stay At Home
description: When active, tamed pets can only go to and cannot leave the owner's home island.

name: Piston Push Protection
description: Enable this to prevent pistons from pushing blocks outside island

name: Potion throwing
description: Toggle throwing potions. This include splash and lingering potions.

name: Prevent teleport when falling
description: Prevent players from teleporting back to their island using commands if they are falling.

name: Remove end exit island
description: Prevents the end exit island from generating at coordinates 0,0

name: Remove monsters
description: Remove monsters when teleporting to island

name: Spawn eggs on spawners
description: Allows to change a spawner's entity type using spawn eggs.

name: TNT damage
description: Allow TNT and TNT minecarts to break blocks and damage entities.

name: TNT priming
description: Prevents priming TNT. It does not override the Flint and steel protection.

name: Trees growing outside range
description: Toggle whether trees can grow outside an island's protection range or not. Not only will it prevent saplings placed outside an island's protection range from growing, but it will also block generation of leaves/logs outside of the island, thus cutting the tree.

name: Visitors keep inventory on death
description: Prevent players from losing their items and experience if they die on an island in which they are a visitor. Island members still lose their items if they die on their own island!

name: Visitors triggers raids
description: Toggles if visitors can start a raid on an island which they are visiting. Bad Omen effect will be removed!

name: Toggle wither damage
description: If active, withers can damage blocks and players

name: World block explode damage
description: Allow Bed & Respawn Anchors to break blocks and damage entities outside of island limits.

name: Move Box
description: Toggle who can move the box with EnderPearls

name: Allow Move Box
description: Toggle if box can be moved with EnderPearls

name: Sky Walker
description: Toggles the ability to walk on the top of the cave world without extra permissions.

name: Island Bank Access
description: Allow access to the island bank.

name: Biome control
description: Toggle who can change the island biome.

name: Biome Island limitation
description: Toggle requirement for players to be on their island to change biome.

name: Cauldron Witchery Protection
description: Toggle who can use cauldron witchery on this island.

name: Challenges Island limitation
description: Toggle requirement for players to be on their island to complete a challenge

name: Fly prevention
description: Toggle who can fly on your island.

name: Magic Generator
description: Toggle to enable or disable all Magic Generators on the whole island.

name: Magic Generator Permissions
description: Select who can activate and deactivate generators.

name: Visit protection
description: Toggle if island can be visited by anyone.

name: Receive Visiting Messages
description: Toggle if members should receive a message if someone visits their island.

name: Void world teleports
description: This allows to toggle ability to teleport to different dimension if player falls in void.

name: Place Warp
description: Allows to toggle who can place warp signs on island
